nodes.text: Ribuk was a male Dug who lived during the waning years of the Galactic Republic.
Ribuk was born on Malastare and became a swoop racer. During the Clone Wars, he competed in the Cularin Classic race, on the planet Cularin.
Ribuk was very competitive and would do everything possible to try and win races. He was willing to "bump" the swoops of other competitors if he believed it would give him and advantage in a race.
